  "description": {
    "zh": "这次任务我建议你同时携带两把武器：雷明顿 Model 700 和 Model 870。你可以在 M870 上安装短枪管和握把，不过不一定非要用两把枪击杀目标——当然，如果你想用也可以\n\n无论如何，你的任务是干掉几个干员，带上他们的狗牌，然后前往森林中的 USEC 营地，把这两把枪藏在那里。明白了吗？",
    "en": "Alright, for this task I recommend you wield both weapons at the same time, you need to use a remington model 700 and model 870. You can use a short barrel and grip on the M870, however, you don't need to kill your targets with both guns, you have the option to however.\nAnyway, take down a few operators, bring their dogtags and after you're done, visit the USEC camp in the forest and hide both weapons there."
  },
